    &lt;dependency&gt;
       &lt;groupId&gt;jakarta.servlet&lt;/groupId&gt;
       &lt;artifactId&gt;jakarta.servlet-api&lt;/artifactId&gt;
       &lt;version&gt;5.0.0&lt;/version&gt;
       &lt;scope&gt;provided&lt;/scope&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;

 
according to Tomcat website: &quot;There is a significant breaking change between Tomcat 9.0.x and Tomcat 10.0.x. The Java package used by the specification APIs has changed from javax... to jakarta.... It will be necessary to recompile web applications against the new APIs.&quot;

